  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc2\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbf\u0b95 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Talks with Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Dammika Perera on Expansion of Chinese Projects in Sri Lanka",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Chi Chenhong has held discussions with Minister for Technology and Investment Promotion Tammika Perera regarding the expansion of Chinese projects in Sri Lanka.",
        "Encouraging Chinese investment was discussed during a recent meeting between Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Xi Senhong and Minister of Technology and Investment Promotion Tammika Perera at the Chinese Embassy in Colombo.",
        "A gazette notification was issued last week to bring significant structures under Dammika Perera's Ministry of Technology and Investment Promotion, including some projects being carried out in Sri Lanka with Chinese funding.",
        "Accordingly, Minister Thammika Perera has been entrusted with the challenging responsibility of promoting foreign investment and private investment in Sri Lanka, which is facing a massive economic crisis.",
        "It is in this context that the meeting with the Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka discussed the promotion of Chinese investment in Sri Lanka and the expansion of existing projects."
      ],
